Having a 16k EPROM for PRG and not mirror anything should work just fine. Yeah, using no mapper is a NROM card, I don't know if there is much difference between NROM-256 and NROM-128. I think NROM-256 has just one more line to the PRG bus.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38">Bregalad</a> — Wed Nov 30, 2005 10:58 am</p><hr />
